  <data name="Faq1Question" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Can I upgrade or downgrade my plan anytime?</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Faq1Answer" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Yes! You can upgrade or downgrade your plan at any time. When upgrading, you'll get immediate access to new features. When downgrading, changes take effect at the end of your billing cycle.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Faq2Question" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>What happens after the 30-day trial?</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Faq2Answer" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>After your trial ends, you can continue with the Free plan or choose a paid plan. Your data is always preserved, and you won't lose any information.</value>
  </data>
