    <value>Do I need a credit card to start?</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Faq3Answer" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>No credit card required to start your free trial. You only need to add payment details when you decide to upgrade to a paid plan.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Faq4Question" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Can I get a refund if I'm not satisfied?</value>
  </data>
